00:22:43,946 --> 00:22:45,013
<font color=#FFFF00>Ada apa?</font>

365
00:22:46,148 --> 00:22:47,249
<font color=#FFFF00>Tidak ada.</font>

366
00:22:47,883 --> 00:22:49,184
<font color=#FFFF00>Apa dia masih di sini?</font>

367
00:22:49,184 --> 00:22:51,153
<font color=#FFFF00>Dia disini. Disini./ Disini?</font>

368
00:22:51,153 --> 00:22:53,655
<font color=#FFFF00>Tidak, geser sedikit.</font>

369
00:22:53,655 --> 00:22:55,290
<font color=#FFFF00>Itu dia.</font>

370
00:23:03,298 --> 00:23:04,466
<font color=#FFFF00>Min Ah.</font>

371
00:23:05,834 --> 00:23:07,970
<font color=#FFFF00>Aku Detektif Cha Dong Tak.</font>

372
00:23:10,439 --> 00:23:12,775
<font color=#FFFF00>Jika aku menangkap pacarmu, aku perlu...</font>

373
00:23:13,542 --> 00:23:14,877
<font color=#FFFF00>...pernyataanmu.</font>

374
00:23:18,847 --> 00:23:19,982
<font color=#FFFF00>Apa yang dia katakan?</font>

375
00:23:21,150 --> 00:23:23,352
<font color=#FFFF00>Tidak ada. Dia tidak akan bicara
sepatah katapun.</font>

376
00:23:25,320 --> 00:23:26,855
<font color=#FFFF00>Apa dia sungguh di sini?</font>

377
00:23:27,189 --> 00:23:29,291
<font color=#FFFF00>Jika kau menipuku.../ Hentikan.</font>

378
00:23:30,292 --> 00:23:32,394
<font color=#FFFF00>Kenapa kau menangis lagi?</font>

379
00:23:33,195 --> 00:23:36,832
<font color=#FFFF00>Bisa berhenti menangis? Kau terlihat sangat sedih.</font>

380
00:23:37,332 --> 00:23:38,700
<font color=#FFFF00>Apa yang terjadi?</font>

381
00:23:39,168 --> 00:23:40,302
<font color=#FFFF00>Lihat?</font>

382
00:23:40,402 --> 00:23:42,438
<font color=#FFFF00>Dia hanya menangis.</font>

383
00:23:44,606 --> 00:23:45,774
<font color=#FFFF00>Jangan menangis.</font>

384
00:23:50,379 --> 00:23:51,980
<font color=#FFFF00>Apa Anda mengingat hal lain?</font>

385
00:23:51,980 --> 00:23:54,983
<font color=#FFFF00>Tunggu, jika diingat lagi,</font>

386
00:23:55,384 --> 00:23:58,387
<font color=#FFFF00>Kadang aku mendengar pertengkaran hebat.</font>

387
00:23:58,387 --> 00:24:00,022
<font color=#FFFF00>Mereka sangat berisik.</font>

388
00:24:00,088 --> 00:24:02,191
<font color=#FFFF00>Hei! Kau gila...</font>

389
00:24:02,224 --> 00:24:04,293
<font color=#FFFF00>Kenapa kau tidak mau dengar?</font>

390
00:24:04,293 --> 00:24:05,594
<font color=#FFFF00>Lepaskan./ Hei.</font>

391
00:24:05,994 --> 00:24:07,529
<font color=#FFFF00>Hei kau...</font>

392
00:24:07,529 --> 00:24:09,298
<font color=#FFFF00>Dia selalu memiliki...</font>

393
00:24:09,298 --> 00:24:11,600
<font color=#FFFF00>...memar di tubuhnya.</font>

394
00:24:11,600 --> 00:24:13,001
<font color=#FFFF00>Kau tidak akan mendengarku?</font>

395
00:24:13,035 --> 00:24:14,736
<font color=#FFFF00>Kenapa Anda tidak melaporkannya?</font>

396
00:24:14,736 --> 00:24:16,271
<font color=#FFFF00>Itu urusan mereka.</font>

397
00:24:17,806 --> 00:24:19,408
<font color=#FFFF00>Dia pernah bilang...</font>

398
00:24:19,408 --> 00:24:23,345
<font color=#FFFF00>...temannya korban kekerasan kencan.</font>

399
00:24:23,345 --> 00:24:25,280
<font color=#FFFF00>Apa yang dia katakan padamu?</font>

400
00:24:25,280 --> 00:24:29,751
<font color=#FFFF00>Salah satu temanku dipukul oleh pacarnya.</font>

401
00:24:30,185 --> 00:24:31,620
<font color=#FFFF00>Bagaimana menurutmu?</font>

402
00:24:31,620 --> 00:24:33,222
<font color=#FFFF00>Bagaimana apanya?</font>

403
00:24:33,255 --> 00:24:34,890
<font color=#FFFF00>Itu namanya bodoh.</font>

404
00:24:34,890 --> 00:24:36,992
<font color=#FFFF00>Itu kesalahan korban.</font>

405
00:24:37,125 --> 00:24:41,029
<font color=#FFFF00>Aku menyebut temannya bodoh karena
tidak meninggalkan pacarnya yang kejam.</font>

406
00:24:41,663 --> 00:24:42,965
<font color=#FFFF00>Aku tidak ingat kapan,</font>

407
00:24:43,198 --> 00:24:45,467
<font color=#FFFF00>...tapi aku melihatnya beberapa kali
di luar kantor patroli kami.</font>

408
00:24:56,445 --> 00:24:58,947
<font color=#FFFF00>Dia tampak ingin membuat laporan.</font>

409
00:24:59,648 --> 00:25:01,016
<font color=#FFFF00>Haruskah aku bertanya waktu itu?</font>

410
00:26:01,310 --> 00:26:03,045
<font color=#FFFF00>Menakutkan bagi roh untuk
melihat roh lain.</font>

411
00:26:03,278 --> 00:26:05,447
<font color=#FFFF00>Sudah berminggu-minggu, dan aku masih belum terbiasa.</font>

412
00:26:06,114 --> 00:26:07,182
<font color=#FFFF00>Ini mengerikan.</font>

413
00:26:08,784 --> 00:26:11,420
<font color=#FFFF00>Aku sungguh melakukan yang terbaik.</font>

414
00:26:11,420 --> 00:26:12,988
<font color=#FFFF00>Jangan salahkan aku nanti.</font>

415
00:26:12,988 --> 00:26:14,189
<font color=#FFFF00>Masuk ke tubuhku.</font>

416
00:26:15,624 --> 00:26:16,792
<font color=#FFFF00>Apa?</font>

417
00:26:18,193 --> 00:26:19,595
<font color=#FFFF00>Masuk ke dalam tubuhku.</font>

418
00:26:21,897 --> 00:26:23,031
<font color=#FFFF00>Wanita itu.</font>

419
00:26:23,398 --> 00:26:25,367
<font color=#FFFF00>Dia datang menemuiku sebelum kejadian ini.</font>

420
00:26:25,367 --> 00:26:27,636
<font color=#FFFF00>Dia ingin memberitahuku sesuatu.</font>

421
00:26:28,804 --> 00:26:31,540
<font color=#FFFF00>Jika aku bicara dengannya secara pribadi,
dia mungkin tidak takut.</font>

422
00:26:32,140 --> 00:26:33,241
<font color=#FFFF00>Lalu?</font>

423
00:26:34,943 --> 00:26:36,745
<font color=#FFFF00>Dengarkan ceritanya untukku.</font>

424
00:26:37,613 --> 00:26:39,615
<font color=#FFFF00>Dan yakinkan dia untuk bangun.</font>

425
00:26:44,386 --> 00:26:45,487
<font color=#FFFF00>Sebagai gantinya,</font>

426
00:26:46,054 --> 00:26:47,656
<font color=#FFFF00>...begitu kasusnya selesai,</font>

427
00:26:47,656 --> 00:26:49,791
<font color=#FFFF00>...segera tinggalkan tubuhku. Itulah syaratnya.</font>

428
00:26:49,825 --> 00:26:53,362
<font color=#FFFF00>Bagaimana caraku meninggalkan tubuhmu?</font>

429
00:26:53,595 --> 00:26:56,565
<font color=#FFFF00>Kau sudah tahu. Kau hanya perlu darah.</font>

430
00:26:56,565 --> 00:26:58,934
<font color=#FFFF00>Donor darahmu, atau benturkan kepalamu
dengan sesuatu.</font>

431
00:27:22,357 --> 00:27:23,792
<font color=#FFFF00>Oh, aku merasa hidup.</font>

432
00:27:26,862 --> 00:27:28,397
<font color=#FFFF00>Seorang pria membutuhkan gaya
rambut yang bagus.</font>

433
00:27:28,563 --> 00:27:31,466
<font color=#FFFF00>Agar bisa membujuknya,
aku harus memberi kesan yang baik.</font>

